    "texte_orig": "W-Wait...[1205][001E][SP]Was[SP]he[SP]here[SP]when[SP]the[SP]clock\ntower[SP]was[SP]collapsing?[SP]No...[1205][001E][SP]He's[SP]not\ndead,[SP]is[SP]he!?",
